parameters: I have reached my limit... I had no choice but to obey the witch...
I was stripped of my clothes... and taken somewhere...
[Anastasia] Wh-... Where are you planning to take me? *panting*
[Anastasia] Ah... There's a voice in my head...?!

[Gisellemina] (Yes♪ I just manipulated your hearing a little to block
out the noise~ Well, that would be inconvenient, so I'm speaking to
you through telepathy♥)

[Anastasia] Haa... haa... Wh-... Why would you do such a thing...?
Ugh... Guh... Haa, haa...

[Gisellemina] (Oh my~ Do you think you're in a position to ask such a
thing?)
